entries.femaleVariant: Another gonk who thought fate smiled on him.
Was probably smilin' to himself before he OD'd on Maelstrom's shipment.
Poor bastard. His output's probably out in Albuquerque waitin', unaware little Jero's brain turned to jelly.
S'what you get for samplin' Maelstrom's supply. Strongest shit out there. Nothing else that can fire up their burnt-out synapses.
